    <h2>🎓 For graduates & office staff – how to pick the right agent</h2>
    <p><strong>📌 Non‑technical workflow builders:</strong> Zapier Agents, n8n, or Relevance AI – connect SaaS tools without coding.<br>
    <strong>📌 Personal / executive support:</strong> Lindy AI and Perplexity Comet handle scheduling, research, and email triage like a human assistant.<br>
    <strong>📌 Developers & technical teams:</strong> Claude Code, CrewAI, LangGraph, and Cursor agents are your production‑grade choices.<br>
    <strong>📌 Creative pros:</strong> Luma Agents unify video, image, and audio generation in one agentic pipeline.<br>
    <strong>📌 Researchers & analysts:</strong> Browser Use and Bright Data Agent Browser extract structured web data autonomously.<br>
    <strong>📌 Multi‑agent orchestration:</strong> AutoGen (Microsoft), Kimi Swarm, and Taskade Genesis let you build collaborative swarms.</p>
    
