        💡 <strong>What to watch in 2026:</strong> The convergence of agent frameworks (AutoGen + Semantic Kernel) and open‑weight swarm intelligence (Kimi K2.6 MIT) is lowering the barrier for custom agent deployment. Most platforms now support BYO‑LLM, meaning you can swap providers to control costs and latency.
